    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, roadworthy daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car has been consistently maintained for performance, potential buyers should expect some visible signs of age. The exterior shows minor scratches and paint fading in several areas, and the interior demonstrates typical wear on the upholstery and dashboard. It is an ideal choice for someone seeking a dependable vehicle without the premium cost of a showroom-quality model.",
