    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior presents beautifully, maintaining a glossy finish with only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been kept in impressive order; the seating surfaces are supple and free of significant wear, while every dial, button, and digital interface operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule that ensures a smooth, responsive driving experience. It has recently undergone a full professional detail and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, making it a turnkey choice for a discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality daily driver.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
